ComicInfo.Summary:
As the new Swamp God travels in search of her destiny, this new ongoing series sprouts intriguing twists and tangles. When a killer storm gathers over subzero Alaskan waters, one member of a crab boat's crew decides to take control of their collective destiny. One of the witnesses to the ensuing tragedy is Tefe Holland. It's a chilling confrontation with human nature for the new half-human Swamp God; will she intervene...and if so, how?
